{"opinion":{"isContribuable":false,"votes_total":28,"arguments_yes_count":1,"arguments_no_count":3,"id":140,"created_at":"2015-09-26T21:30:17+0200","updated_at":"2015-09-26T21:31:22+0200","body":"<p>A l&#39;article L. 45-1 du Code &eacute;lectoral, il est ajout&eacute; un dernier alin&eacute;a&nbsp;ainsi r&eacute;dig&eacute;:&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;3&deg; Pendant une dur&eacute;e maximale d&#39;un an, les personnes titulaires d&#39;un mandat &eacute;lectoral qui n&#39;ont pas proc&eacute;d&eacute; au d&eacute;ploiement du tr&egrave;s haut d&eacute;bit dans leur circonscription au 1er janvier 2017&quot;<\/p>","versions_count":0,"sources_count":0,"arguments_count":4,"author":{"username":"Ines","displayName":"Ines","uniqueId":"ines","isAdmin":false,"media":null,"vip":false,"_links":{"profile":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/ines","settings":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/edit-profile"}},"type":{"id":104,"title":"Section 2","subtitle":"Couverture num\u00e9rique","voteWidgetType":2,"votesHelpText":"Pensez-vous que cette proposition permet d'atteindre les objectifs pr\u00e9sent\u00e9s dans l\u2019explication de l\u2019article ?","commentSystem":2,"color":"blue","versionable":true,"sourceable":true,"votesThreshold":null,"votesThresholdHelpText":null},"sources":[],"arguments":[{"isContribuable":false,"id":5454,"body":"Proposition qui part peut-\u00eatre d'un bon sentiment mais qui n'est pas s\u00e9rieuse en l'\u00e9tat du droit et de la pratique. Qui voudra encore \u00eatre maire ?","created_at":"2015-10-17T18:24:18+0200","updated_at":"2015-10-17T18:24:18+0200","is_enabled":true,"votes_count":0,"type":0,"is_trashed":false,"author":{"username":"Tan\u00e9l\u00e9o","displayName":"Tan\u00e9l\u00e9o","uniqueId":"taneleo","isAdmin":false,"media":null,"vip":false,"_links":{"profile":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/taneleo","settings":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/edit-profile"}},"_links":{"show":"https:\/\/